{"acceptance_criteria":"","actor":"","agent_state":"","assignee":null,"await_id":"","await_type":"","close_reason":"Added chezmoi and OMZ plugin checks to weekly workflow, trimmed MAINTENANCE.md. PR #51.","closed_at":"2026-03-01T16:19:20Z","closed_by_session":"","compacted_at":null,"compacted_at_commit":null,"compaction_level":0,"content_hash":null,"created_at":"2026-02-28T16:48:52Z","created_by":"Paul Gledhill","crystallizes":0,"defer_until":null,"description":"Review what maintenance the dotfiles repo needs and how much is already automated. Current automation: (1) package-updates.yml — weekly check for Homebrew outdated + Starship releases, creates GitHub issues. (2) ghostty-terminfo.yml — weekly regeneration of xterm-ghostty terminfo. (3) dependabot.yml — weekly GitHub Actions version bumps. (4) pre-commit — markdownlint-cli2. Gaps to investigate: (a) No automated chezmoi version tracking. (b) No Oh My Zsh plugin update detection. (c) No shell startup time regression monitoring. (d) No automated apt/winget package freshness checks (only Homebrew). (e) docs/MAINTENANCE.md describes monthly/quarterly/annual tasks but none are automated or tracked. (f) No Brewfile.lock or pinned versions for reproducibility. Propose which gaps are worth filling and how (GitHub Actions, chezmoi hooks, or manual checklist).","design":"","due_at":null,"ephemeral":0,"estimated_minutes":null,"event_kind":"","external_ref":null,"hook_bead":"","id":"dotfiles-qqw","is_template":0,"issue_type":"task","last_activity":null,"metadata":"{}","mol_type":"","notes":"","original_size":null,"owner":"","payload":"","pinned":0,"priority":2,"quality_score":null,"rig":"","role_bead":"","role_type":"","sender":"","source_repo":"","source_system":"","spec_id":null,"status":"closed","target":"","timeout_ns":0,"title":"Investigate and automate maintenance tasks","updated_at":"2026-03-01T16:19:20Z","waiters":"","wisp_type":"","work_type":"mutex"}
